00:10:57,498 --> 00:10:59,057
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati hati./ Terima kasih.</font>

187
00:10:59,197 --> 00:11:01,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga. Terima kasih.</font>

188
00:11:01,398 --> 00:11:02,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

189
00:11:08,868 --> 00:11:10,138
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa banyak royaltinya?</font>

190
00:11:10,738 --> 00:11:12,437
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku rasa banyak.
Dia seorang penyair terkenal.</font>

191
00:11:13,707 --> 00:11:15,847
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak punya anak. Itu akan diberikan kesiapa?</font>

192
00:11:16,648 --> 00:11:18,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau psikopat?</font>

193
00:11:18,748 --> 00:11:21,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau bisa bicara
tentang royalti saat seorang akan meninggal?</font>

194
00:11:21,488 --> 00:11:24,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, karena aku tidak terlahir
kaya seperti yang lain.</font>

195
00:11:24,618 --> 00:11:25,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei.</font>

196
00:11:25,618 --> 00:11:28,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau belajar Pengobatan Korea?</font>

197
00:11:28,988 --> 00:11:29,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

198
00:11:29,988 --> 00:11:32,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau Pengobatan Korea, itu berarti kau
sama sekali tidak berguna di sekolah.</font>

199
00:11:33,197 --> 00:11:34,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa tidak sekolah kedokteran?</font>

200
00:11:35,467 --> 00:11:36,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa mewarisi
Rumah Sakit Ayahmu.</font>

201
00:11:40,067 --> 00:11:41,508
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada orang lain yang mewarisinya.</font>

202
00:11:43,467 --> 00:11:44,908
<font color=#FFFF00>Ketika aku pertama masuk sekolah,</font>

203
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:47,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang di tahun pertama,
dan aku membencinya.</font>

204
00:11:48,577 --> 00:11:49,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa?</font>

205
00:11:51,518 --> 00:11:52,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Kakakmu?</font>

206
00:11:54,447 --> 00:11:56,347
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau berbicara
masa lalu dengan kesal?</font>

207
00:11:56,817 --> 00:11:57,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia berhenti minum obat?</font>

208
00:11:58,957 --> 00:12:00,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, dia meninggal.</font>

209
00:12:02,288 --> 00:12:03,357
<font color=#FFFF00>Kecelakaan mobil...</font>

210
00:12:03,788 --> 00:12:06,528
<font color=#FFFF00>...saat menuju Bandara
untuk menjemputku.</font>

211
00:12:08,227 --> 00:12:10,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau bicara
seperti dia orang asing?</font>

212
00:12:11,498 --> 00:12:12,538
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu aku harus bagaimana?</font>

213
00:12:13,038 --> 00:12:14,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus menangis?</font>

214
00:12:15,868 --> 00:12:16,908
<font color=#FFFF00>Lupakan.</font>

215
00:12:18,038 --> 00:12:19,077
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tidak menyenangkan.
Ayo pergi.</font>

216
00:12:22,077 --> 00:12:23,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Royalti.</font>

217
00:12:24,107 --> 00:12:26,077
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena dia tidak punya anak...</font>

218
00:12:26,077 --> 00:12:28,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa berhenti?</font>

219
00:12:32,118 --> 00:12:33,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa dia terlihat kecewa?</font>

220
00:12:35,758 --> 00:12:37,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terlihat sangat menyedihkan.</font>

221
00:12:38,357 --> 00:12:40,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang akan mengira
kau menunggu pacarmu.</font>

222
00:12:40,758 --> 00:12:42,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau suka bercanda?/ Iya.</font>

223
00:12:47,197 --> 00:12:48,408
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[dr. Song]</i></font>

224
00:12:59,118 --> 00:13:00,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru.</font>

225
00:13:00,317 --> 00:13:01,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah selesai?</font>

226
00:13:02,048 --> 00:13:04,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar lagi.</font>

227
00:13:04,187 --> 00:13:05,187
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo makan.</font>

228
00:13:06,957 --> 00:13:09,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya, tunggu.</font>

229
00:13:09,357 --> 00:13:10,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Akhirnya.</font>

230
00:13:10,998 --> 00:13:12,158
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku selesai.</font>

231
00:13:19,298 --> 00:13:21,437
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini./ Baunya harum.</font>

232
00:13:26,278 --> 00:13:27,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin ini tidak enak.</font>

233
00:13:32,648 --> 00:13:35,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Rasanya bahkan lebih
luar biasa.</font>

234
00:13:35,048 --> 00:13:38,057
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh?/ Tentu. Ayo makan.</font>

235
00:13:42,587 --> 00:13:44,528
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanlah dengan lahap.</font>

236
00:13:44,528 --> 00:13:46,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah itu pulang
naik kapal terakhir.</font>

237
00:13:46,557 --> 00:13:48,028
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan tidur disini.</font>

238
00:13:51,738 --> 00:13:53,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa aku akan meninggal
malam ini?</font>

239
00:13:53,998 --> 00:13:55,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau bisa
mengatakan itu?</font>

240
00:13:56,368 --> 00:13:58,677
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu mengapa kau memperlakukanku
seperti akan meninggal?</font>

241
00:14:00,408 --> 00:14:02,878
<font color=#FFFF00>Banyak pekerjaan yang
harus kulakukan.</font>

242
00:14:02,878 --> 00:14:04,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan mengganggu konsentrasiku,</font>

243
00:14:04,317 --> 00:14:07,118
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan aku akan sibuk jika kau disini.</font>

244
00:14:08,118 --> 00:14:11,087
<font color=#FFFF00>Semalam saja. Biarkan aku menginap semalam.</font>

245
00:14:11,288 --> 00:14:13,057
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan Rumah Sakit Kapal?</font>

246
00:14:13,057 --> 00:14:14,457
<font color=#FFFF00>Antar aku pakai perahu sekolah.</font>

247
00:14:14,457 --> 00:14:16,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tidak jauh.</font>

248
00:14:17,128 --> 00:14:20,057
<font color=#FFFF00>Semalam saja./ Baik.</font>

249
00:15:08,807 --> 00:15:10,107
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa tidur?</font>

250
00:15:11,518 --> 00:15:12,577
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

251
00:15:13,518 --> 00:15:15,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu akan terjadi saat kau tua.</font>

252
00:15:17,788 --> 00:15:19,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau takut?</font>

253
00:15:24,827 --> 00:15:27,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini pertama kalinya
aku sekarat, jadi...</font>

254
00:15:30,837 --> 00:15:32,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bisa melawannya.</font>

255
00:15:34,707 --> 00:15:37,778
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa kembali ke Rumah Sakit
dan menjalani operasi,</font>

256
00:15:38,077 --> 00:15:40,008
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau kita bisa mencari Dokter lain.</font>

257
00:15:42,207 --> 00:15:44,217
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi satu hal yang pasti,</font>

258
00:15:45,118 --> 00:15:47,317
<font color=#FFFF00>...apapun keputusanmu,</font>

259
00:15:48,648 --> 00:15:49,947
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku akan bersamamu.</font>

260
00:15:51,618 --> 00:15:53,217
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan tetap bersamamu.</font>

261
00:16:20,378 --> 00:16:21,687
<font color=#FFFF00>Darimana saja kau?</font>

262
00:16:22,187 --> 00:16:25,687
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau bersama pasien
tadi malam?</font>

263
00:16:26,388 --> 00:16:28,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau tidak
mengangkat telponku?</font>

264
00:16:29,758 --> 00:16:30,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa artinya itu?</font>

265
00:16:30,998 --> 00:16:33,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terlihat seperti istri yang
mengomel suaminya karena tidak pulang.</font>

266
00:16:34,427 --> 00:16:36,128
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin bercanda.</font>

267
00:16:36,868 --> 00:16:38,837
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pasien baik-baik saja?</font>

268
00:16:58,317 --> 00:16:59,357
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?</font>

269
00:16:59,357 --> 00:17:02,628
<font color=#FFFF00>Tesis yang sedang aku kerjakan.
Meski belum selesai...</font>

270
00:17:05,298 --> 00:17:08,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan ini hasil
tes pada hewan.</font>

271
00:17:09,327 --> 00:17:11,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Dalam beberapa hal, tes pada
hewan jauh lebih sulit.</font>

272
00:17:11,897 --> 00:17:13,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Anjing mungkin tampak lebih
kuat dari manusia,</font>

273
00:17:13,798 --> 00:17:15,538
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi mereka jauh lebih lemah.</font>

274
00:17:15,538 --> 00:17:18,738
<font color=#FFFF00>Intinya, jika berhasil
pada anjing, manusia...</font>

275
00:17:18,738 --> 00:17:20,577
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan. Sudah cukup.</font>

276
00:17:24,077 --> 00:17:25,377
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

277
00:17:26,948 --> 00:17:28,647
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa menurutmu ini akan
membuat pasien yakin?</font>

278
00:17:28,647 --> 00:17:31,087
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien takut karena ini
operasi pertama kali.</font>

279
00:17:31,087 --> 00:17:34,018
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi kita harus meyakinkannya.../
Dengan data tes pada hewan?</font>

280
00:17:35,758 --> 00:17:37,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingat nama pasien
pertama operasimu?</font>

281
00:17:38,097 --> 00:17:39,657
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa nama pasien pertamamu?</font>

282
00:17:40,528 --> 00:17:41,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak ingat, 'kan?</font>

283
00:17:42,127 --> 00:17:44,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa melihat operasi dengan jelas,
seolah-olah sebagai foto,</font>

284
00:17:44,468 --> 00:17:46,298
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi kau tidak tahu nama pasien,</font>

285
00:17:46,597 --> 00:17:50,268
<font color=#FFFF00>...fisik, perjuangan sebelum operasi,
dan hal-hal seperti itu, 'kan?</font>

286
00:17:50,367 --> 00:17:51,607
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa salahnya?</font>

287
00:17:51,607 --> 00:17:53,607
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah mengapa kau
seperti ini.</font>

288
00:17:54,178 --> 00:17:56,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu apa itu kepercayaan?</font>

289
00:17:56,248 --> 00:17:58,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu membuat orang merasa yakin,</font>

290
00:17:58,248 --> 00:18:01,087
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukan hanya memegang data dan
mengatakan apa yang kau mau.</font>

291
00:18:01,288 --> 00:18:03,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus mendengarnya dulu.</font>

292
00:18:03,248 --> 00:18:06,758
<font color=#FFFF00>"Apa yang dia inginkan?
Apa yang dia takuti?"</font>

293
00:18:06,917 --> 00:18:08,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak memikirkan itu, 'kan?</font>

294
00:18:08,887 --> 00:18:11,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena bagimu, pasien hanyalah alat...</font>

295
00:18:11,228 --> 00:18:13,057
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk menuju kesuksesanmu.</font>

296
00:18:13,057 --> 00:18:14,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Menjadi dokter adalah
tugas kita.</font>

297
00:18:16,597 --> 00:18:18,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengobati pasien juga
tugas kita.</font>

298
00:18:18,968 --> 00:18:21,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita dibayar untuk itu.</font>

299
00:18:21,968 --> 00:18:23,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu salah?</font>

300
00:18:23,538 --> 00:18:26,077
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik. Anggap saja...</font>

301
00:18:26,607 --> 00:18:28,347
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku pecandu yang terobsesi
pada kesuksesan,</font>

302
00:18:28,347 --> 00:18:30,877
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang lebih peduli dengan karir
daripada hidup pasien?</font>

303
00:18:32,077 --> 00:18:34,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

304
00:18:34,688 --> 00:18:37,587
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mencoba menyelesaikannya,
tapi intinya,</font>

305
00:18:37,587 --> 00:18:39,657
<font color=#FFFF00>...ada pasien sekarat di depanmu,</font>

306
00:18:40,357 --> 00:18:42,928
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi kau tidak melakukan apapun.</font>

307
00:18:44,327 --> 00:18:46,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan kau sebut dirimu dokter?/
Dokter.</font>

308
00:19:02,208 --> 00:19:05,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak boleh kesana./
Dan kau tidak boleh naik.</font>

309
00:19:10,448 --> 00:19:12,587
<font color=#FFFF00>Kohabitasi artinya...</font>

310
00:19:12,587 --> 00:19:15,657
<font color=#FFFF00>...kalian ada aturan. Aturan.</font>

311
00:19:15,657 --> 00:19:16,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Terutama kau, dr. Song.</font>

312
00:19:16,788 --> 00:19:18,857
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kau masih baru dan
bekerja di UGD,</font>

313
00:19:18,857 --> 00:19:21,097
<font color=#FFFF00>...kami selama ini sudah sabar.</font>

314
00:19:21,097 --> 00:19:24,738
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi sekarang, kami ingin kau
juga berpartisipasi.</font>

315
00:19:24,738 --> 00:19:25,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

316
00:19:26,798 --> 00:19:27,807
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Aturan Asrama Rumah Sakit Kapal]</i></font>

317
00:19:33,038 --> 00:19:35,147
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Aturan Asrama Rumah Sakit Kapal]</i></font>

318
00:19:35,147 --> 00:19:36,508
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang harus aku lakukan?</font>

319
00:19:37,278 --> 00:19:38,847
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini.</font>

320
00:19:39,548 --> 00:19:40,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemari.</font>

321
00:19:41,788 --> 00:19:43,448
<font color=#FFFF00>Main tangga?/
Ya, main tangga.</font>

322
00:19:43,448 --> 00:19:45,657
<font color=#FFFF00>Beginilah cara kami memilih./
Ini murni keberuntungan.</font>

323
00:19:45,657 --> 00:19:46,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Oke?/ Nomor satu.</font>

324
00:19:46,958 --> 00:19:47,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Sembilan./ Dua.</font>

325
00:19:47,958 --> 00:19:49,087
<font color=#FFFF00>Empat./ Enam.</font>

326
00:19:49,087 --> 00:19:50,157
<font color=#FFFF00>Lima./ Delapan.</font>

327
00:19:50,157 --> 00:19:51,557
<font color=#FFFF00>Tiga./ Tujuh.</font>

328
00:19:55,728 --> 00:19:58,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes./ Semoga tidak kamar mandi.</font>

329
00:20:00,738 --> 00:20:02,307
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamar mandi lagi?</font>

330
00:20:02,307 --> 00:20:04,178
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus memandikan Bong Gu.</font>

331
00:20:04,178 --> 00:20:07,478
<font color=#FFFF00>dr. Song dapat... belanja?</font>

332
00:20:07,478 --> 00:20:09,778
<font color=#FFFF00>Beruntungnya.</font>

333
00:20:10,577 --> 00:20:12,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau belanja juga?</font>

334
00:20:17,147 --> 00:20:18,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Tukar denganku./
Apa yang dia katakan?</font>

335
00:20:18,988 --> 00:20:20,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah. Jangan berkelahi.</font>

336
00:20:20,788 --> 00:20:24,028
<font color=#FFFF00>dr. Kwak. Ini daftarnya.</font>

337
00:20:24,327 --> 00:20:26,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sudah diputuskan.</font>

338
00:20:32,998 --> 00:20:34,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Daftar belanja.</font>

339
00:21:30,428 --> 00:21:33,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingat semuanya dengan
sekali lihat...</font>

340
00:21:34,567 --> 00:21:36,228
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan selesai dalam 10 menit?</font>

341
00:21:36,397 --> 00:21:38,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada bedanya dengan
menghafal buku pembuluh darah.</font>

342
00:21:40,538 --> 00:21:41,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa lagi selanjutnya?</font>

343
00:21:42,968 --> 00:21:44,807
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Coba juga ini.</i></font>

344
00:21:44,807 --> 00:21:47,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membeli ini.
Biar aku coba.</font>

345
00:21:51,478 --> 00:21:52,647
<font color=#FFFF00>Enak?</font>

346
00:21:52,748 --> 00:21:55,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, enak./ 20 dolar.</font>

347
00:21:55,248 --> 00:21:58,387
<font color=#FFFF00>Beri diskon.
Aku beli banyak.</font>

348
00:21:58,387 --> 00:21:59,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Beli apa lagi?</font>

349
00:22:02,087 --> 00:22:05,057
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikan apa yang enak untuk direbus?/
Semuanya enak.</font>

350
00:22:05,057 --> 00:22:07,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikan batu, usus ikan,
dan cumi asin pedas.</font>

351
00:22:07,357 --> 00:22:09,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Kerang lebih enak.</font>

352
00:22:09,298 --> 00:22:11,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Hidup tidak selalu berjalan
sesuai rencana.</font>

353
00:22:14,238 --> 00:22:15,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

354
00:22:17,307 --> 00:22:18,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak lihat daftar ini?</font>

355
00:22:19,107 --> 00:22:21,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo. Suamimu benar.</font>

356
00:22:21,807 --> 00:22:24,278
<font color=#FFFF00>Istri./ Aku bukan istrinya.</font>

357
00:22:24,278 --> 00:22:26,377
<font color=#FFFF00>Datanglah ke mobil lima menit lagi,
atau aku pergi.</font>

358
00:22:26,478 --> 00:22:27,817
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau punya kunci mobil?</font>

359
00:22:33,258 --> 00:22:34,357
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa itu...</font>

360
00:22:35,857 --> 00:22:38,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti istrimu. Kalian bertengkar?</font>

361
00:22:39,097 --> 00:22:40,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akting, 'kan?</font>

362
00:22:41,798 --> 00:22:44,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membeli ini dan itu.</font>

363
00:22:44,567 --> 00:22:47,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo. Sangat sulit mencari nafkah.</font>

364
00:22:47,708 --> 00:22:49,538
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan memberimu banyak./
Terima kasih.</font>

365
00:22:52,377 --> 00:22:53,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo...</font>

366
00:22:56,647 --> 00:22:58,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau belum mengambilnya...</font>

367
00:23:02,248 --> 00:23:03,587
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi?</font>

368
00:23:05,188 --> 00:23:06,317
